$ %PROGRAMFILES%\Microsoft Office\root\Templates

`%PROGRAMFILES%\Microsoft Office\root\Templates` and its subdirectories contain templates for → Microsoft/Office applications that are available for all
→ Windows/user-account[users] on a computer.

This directory as well as its subdirectories is in the default list of → Microsoft/Office/security/Trust-Center/Trusted-Locations for
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel, → Microsoft/Office/Word and → Microsoft/Office/PowerPoint.

Files that are found in this directory include → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Templates/Normal_dotm[`Normal.dotm`]

sa:
  Templates that are only available to a specific user are stored in → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Templates.
